40|$|Over {{the last}} few years, there have been five best sellers {{critical}} of religion and <b>religious</b> <b>belief.</b> It seems that there is great interest in questions about <b>religious</b> <b>belief.</b> Ironically, critical thinking texts seldom examine the topic. This paper will evaluate eight arguments to exempt <b>religious</b> <b>belief</b> from rational critique. I conclude that the topic of <b>religious</b> <b>belief</b> should not be exempt from critical thinking classes...|$|R
